00:12:17.510 --> 00:12:19.560 align:middle line:90%
But that place was so amazing.

00:12:19.560 --> 00:12:22.520 align:middle line:84%
It was so hard to
leave that realm.

00:12:22.520 --> 00:12:26.720 align:middle line:84%
But then I started
to understand why

00:12:26.720 --> 00:12:30.640 align:middle line:84%
I got the cancer, why
everything that had happened,

00:12:30.640 --> 00:12:31.560 align:middle line:90%
happened to me.

00:12:31.560 --> 00:12:36.080 align:middle line:84%
I had this incredible-- like
it was a clarity, that I knew

00:12:36.080 --> 00:12:41.700 align:middle line:84%
exactly what it was that had
led me to that point in time

00:12:41.700 --> 00:12:42.400 align:middle line:90%
in my life.

