00:13:02.070 --> 00:13:05.030 align:middle line:84%
that now that I understood
what caused my cancer,

00:13:05.030 --> 00:13:08.250 align:middle line:84%
I would no longer
have the cancer.

00:13:08.250 --> 00:13:11.650 align:middle line:84%
And I understood
that we as humans,

00:13:11.650 --> 00:13:17.310 align:middle line:84%
that I was an amazing human
being, that we all are.

00:13:17.310 --> 00:13:20.370 align:middle line:84%
We are all amazing
spiritual beings.

00:13:20.370 --> 00:13:25.390 align:middle line:84%
But I had never allowed my
magnificence to flow through.

00:13:25.390 --> 00:13:28.020 align:middle line:84%
I had always suppressed
it out of fear.

00:13:28.020 --> 00:13:31.870 align:middle line:84%
And I understood that all I
had to do was to come back

00:13:31.870 --> 00:13:35.720 align:middle line:84%
and to allow myself to be
the magnificence that I am.

00:13:35.720 --> 00:13:38.700 align:middle line:84%
And that was all I had to
do and my body would heal.

00:13:38.700 --> 00:13:39.990 align:middle line:90%
Just showing up.

