It's like out of prison.

00:13:51.960 --> 00:13:53.420 align:middle line:84%
Oh, yeah.
It is.

00:13:53.420 --> 00:13:54.900 align:middle line:90%
More than one way for you.

00:13:54.900 --> 00:13:56.740 align:middle line:90%
Yeah, it really is.

00:13:56.740 --> 00:13:58.450 align:middle line:90%
It's like being out of prison.

00:13:58.450 --> 00:13:59.960 align:middle line:90%
It so is.

