Your dad, you had a good
relationship with your dad

00:14:19.260 --> 00:14:20.790 align:middle line:90%
while growing up?

00:14:20.790 --> 00:14:24.180 align:middle line:84%
Because you were
raised in Hong Kong?

00:14:24.180 --> 00:14:25.860 align:middle line:84%
Yeah, I was raised
in Hong Kong.

00:14:25.860 --> 00:14:30.710 align:middle line:84%
My parents are Hindu,
Indian by race.

00:14:30.710 --> 00:14:34.640 align:middle line:84%
And my father and I had
