I didn't want an
arranged marriage.

00:15:01.220 --> 00:15:04.020 align:middle line:84%
So we used to
clash all the time.

00:15:04.020 --> 00:15:07.880 align:middle line:90%
And we had very different ideas.

00:15:07.880 --> 00:15:11.720 align:middle line:84%
But the interesting thing
