00:15:23.090 --> 00:15:26.480 align:middle line:84%
physical, nothing
biological about us

00:15:26.480 --> 00:15:29.430 align:middle line:90%
at all, no ego no culture.

00:15:29.430 --> 00:15:34.030 align:middle line:84%
We were just pure spirit,
pure consciousness.

00:15:34.030 --> 00:15:37.410 align:middle line:84%
And all I could
feel from him was

00:15:37.410 --> 00:15:40.040 align:middle line:84%
unconditional
