00:15:50.030 --> 00:15:53.970 align:middle line:84%
But when we express ourselves
through our physical bodies,

00:15:53.970 --> 00:15:57.810 align:middle line:84%
our biology, our culture,
our beliefs, our values,

00:15:57.810 --> 00:16:00.810 align:middle line:90%
it kind of filters that love.

00:16:00.810 --> 00:16:03.600 align:middle line:84%
And so my father had
loved me in the best way

00:16:03.600 --> 00:16:07.250 align:middle line:84%
