I'm already healed.

00:18:46.600 --> 00:18:47.440 align:middle line:90%
That's why I'm back.

00:18:47.440 --> 00:18:49.150 align:middle line:90%
That's why I'm awake.

00:18:49.150 --> 00:18:50.780 align:middle line:84%
And where do you
