It comes from an inner knowing.

00:18:55.590 --> 00:19:00.750 align:middle line:84%
And I think that if we get in
touch with our consciousness,

00:19:00.750 --> 00:19:06.320 align:middle line:84%
with our truth, with our heart,
what's in there, and if we get

00:19:06.320 --> 00:19:08.970 align:middle line:84%
in touch with that and
what we get from there,

00:19:08.970 --> 00:19:11.570 align:middle line:90%
