can start to-- actually start

00:20:30.190 --> 00:20:35.810 align:middle line:84%
to stop giving your power
away to external elements,

00:20:35.810 --> 00:20:40.420 align:middle line:84%
external things that brainwash
us-- things like fears

00:20:40.420 --> 00:20:44.380 align:middle line:84%
and feelings of inadequacy
