00:20:44.380 --> 00:20:48.410 align:middle line:84%
taking your power back
and listening to yourself,

00:20:48.410 --> 00:20:50.050 align:middle line:90%
silencing your mind.

00:20:50.050 --> 00:20:52.310 align:middle line:84%
When you silence your
mind, it means silencing

