because who you are
in here is somebody

00:21:11.530 --> 00:21:15.500 align:middle line:84%
who is desperate to feel
joyful and to let it out,

00:21:15.500 --> 00:21:17.530 align:middle line:90%
a magnificent being.

00:21:17.530 --> 00:21:21.590 align:middle line:84%
And once you can get
in touch with that--

